    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the passenger side doors, and some clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat bolster, though all major electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future to be at its best. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
