      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is priced to reflect its current state. While it remains a reliable daily driver, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings on the passenger door, and some fading of the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
