      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. It drives like a dream and is in truly incredible shape. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in immaculate condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically, this chassis has been fastidiously maintained with preventative rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional torque distribution, while the suspension retains its original geometry and damping characteristics. The exterior retains all original VIN-stamped panels with flawless paint depth, and the interior shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. A truly turnkey performance icon for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
