    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior finish boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. The original alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash or pitting, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. Inside, the cabin retains its factory-fresh aroma; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolsters wear or creasing, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships, including a recent comprehensive inspection, oil service, and brake fluid flush. The engine bay is remarkably clean, showing the care this vehicle has received, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or road debris. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. No modifications, no accidents, smoke-free, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
